item.title: PLTR
item.description: score:180 Chances: Palantir has been a popular growth stock for investors bullish on artificial intelligence. Shares of Palantir (PLTR) are moving up as the company announced it won a contract with the US Army valued at $178 million, to build out TITAN (Tactical Intelligence Targeting Access Node) artificial intelligence-enabled ground stations.

item.title: AYX
item.description: score:4 Chances: Alteryx’s fair value estimate is US$56.24, indicating potential for upside. Appointment of Kevin Rubin as Interim CEO could bring positive changes to the company. Risks: Fierce competition from bigger rivals such as Microsoft and Oracle may pose a challenge. Setbacks in winning new business have suppressed Alteryx’s valuation.
